}{TEXT 203 0 "" }}{PARA 206 "" 0 "" {TEXT 205 0 "" }}}{EXCHG {PARA 
208 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 207 47 "N := 200; Nr := 200; rmin := 3.0; rma
