lf(rmin + (rmax - rmin)*i/Nr);" }{MPLTEXT 1 0 0 "" }}{PARA 210 "" 0 ""
 {TEXT 208 7 "       " }{TEXT 209 25 "Calculate the x[n] series" }
{TEXT 208 0 "" }}{PARA 208 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 62 "  for n from 1 t
