 }}}{EXCHG {PARA 211 "" 0 "" {TEXT 201 28 "plot the bifurcation diagra
m" }{TEXT 201 0 "" }}}{EXCHG {PARA 212 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 210 88 "po
